 />\n雖然我覺得課金好on9 佢都知我咁諗<br />\n我食食下飯同佢講 你都係課啦<br />\n我都覺得我唔可以咁專制<br />\n明明自己買多過需要既化妝品護膚品納雜野又得<br />\n相比起下佢用好少錢買娛樂就唔得<br />\n到宜家佢隻game都玩好耐下<br />\n<br />\n希望我以後都可以咁清醒咁諗<br />\n女人結左婚就要為頭家計算<br />\n但人都係寬己嚴人 <br />\n巴打你同老婆傾下啦 我覺得真係有需要既冇理由唔比買"},{"pid":"f8bee99da5fd8bdd244fd5e79c80f0c17be328db","tid":358011,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:04:25.000Z","msg":"幾百蚊都管又誇張咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0700a7ac369f2901c990b5fbb34e03f7c95a2596","tid":358011,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己幾佰幾佰諗都唔諗<br />\n我就買個垃圾桶都唔畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為<br />\n你既錢=佢既錢<br />\n佢既錢=佢既錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真理"},{"pid":"39c5ea41556bcdfc373034362d3749b4897ed139","tid":358011,"uid":7229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"最撚憎呢d 女人控制狂<br />\n如果d 錢佢有份搵都還好，冇既唔該叫佢收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccf7c561043febdc38c25d5b47f8d73ead2f4d7","tid":358011,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7e65828082ba2dcff0520013da26e0c6f9f16c1","tid":358011,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以話呢結婚為左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">養兒防老</span>"},{"pid":"c827fa6e74bf66ab3587256efb634a4a35aecb51","tid":358011,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re