對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主，我真心同你講對唔住<br />\n女人真係好on9，好多嘢唔係所謂想得寸進尺，<br />\n而係好白痴咁以為你好錫佢好錫佢，<br />\n或者唔會講多謝你做咁多嘢，但有你呢個男人可以依靠一直覺得好幸福，<br />\n希望佢一次都唔會發現你曾經係連登鬧佢呀，<br />\n因為咁樣比起你同佢講：「你有公主病咩？八婆！」來得更加心痛，<br />\n代你老婆同你講多幾句對唔住啦我係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你會下咗啖氣唔好擺係心<br />\n下次有咩可以試下心平氣和傾下啦，唔好心入面有條刺</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d8ff4bb2e0aff49d99ee2dd42a1e38181c155b","tid":358011,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從來唔理我"},{"pid":"234d088fc69c2f3851c02425aa0edd1df0641178","tid":358011,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:41:19.000Z","msg":"好掛住紫青巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf08b8a361064efdd51041871d2f025bafcc073a","tid":358011,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:53:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"304360544ba29c07317d07a57fec905325f4e084","tid":358011,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0e495d3c76886cd24c31ddffb05099e6d4b433e","tid":358011,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:59:02.000Z","msg":"同港女結婚"},{"pid":"a8e809ab6d0ac25d2e5e5d766eb25350a6b97439","tid":358011,"uid":14349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一佰幾十買乜撚都話唔好，攪到自己做乜都係錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fro